  "helpFriendsModeBody": "Friends mode troubleshooting tips:\n\n1. Make sure the relay friend account is added/accepted on the console (if required).\n2. Try restarting the game and refreshing the Friends/LAN tab after enabling Friends mode.\n\nIf the server still doesn't appear to friends, enable Debug Mode and check logs to identify errors.",
